{
  "title": "|x² − 4x + 3| = a — ровно 3 решения",
  "canvas": {
    "width": 560,
    "height": 440,
    "x_min": 0,
    "x_max": 4,
    "y_min": -2,
    "y_max": 2,
    "x_label": "x",
    "y_label": "y"
  },
  "steps": [
    {
      "text": "Строим график $y = |x^2 - 4x + 3|$.",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "function_curve",
          "id": "f1",
          "expression": "abs(x**2 - 4*x + 3)",
          "label": "y = |x² − 4x + 3|",
          "style": {
            "stroke": "#2980b9",
            "stroke_width": 2.5
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "**Критические уровни параметра:**\n$a = 0$ — нули функции, $a = 1$ — локальный максимум «отражённой» части.",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "hline",
          "id": "h1",
          "y": 0,
          "label": "a = 0",
          "style": {
            "stroke": "#e74c3c",
            "dash": "dashed"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "hline",
          "id": "h2",
          "y": 1,
          "label": "a = 1",
          "style": {
            "stroke": "#8e44ad",
            "dash": "dashed"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "point",
          "id": "p1",
          "x": 1,
          "y": 0,
          "label": "(1; 0)"
        },
        {
          "type": "point",
          "id": "p2",
          "x": 3,
          "y": 0,
          "label": "(3; 0)"
        },
        {
          "type": "point",
          "id": "p3",
          "x": 2,
          "y": 1,
          "label": "(2; 1)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "Считаем пересечения $y = a$ с графиком:\n- $a < 0$: **0 решений**\n- $a = 0$: **2 решения**\n- $0 < a < 1$: **4 решения**\n- $a = 1$: **3 решения**\n- $a > 1$: **2 решения**",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "region_label",
          "id": "rl1",
          "x": 2,
          "y": -1.5,
          "text": "0 решений",
          "style": {
            "color": "#888",
            "font_size": 13,
            "background": "rgba(255,255,255,0.9)"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "region_label",
          "id": "rl2",
          "x": 2,
          "y": 0.5,
          "text": "2 решения",
          "style": {
            "color": "#e74c3c",
            "font_size": 13,
            "background": "rgba(255,255,255,0.9)"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "region_label",
          "id": "rl3",
          "x": 2,
          "y": 1.5,
          "text": "4 решения",
          "style": {
            "color": "#8e44ad",
            "font_size": 13,
            "background": "rgba(255,255,255,0.9)"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "**Ответ: $a = 1$.**",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "hline",
          "id": "h_answer",
          "y": 1,
          "label": "a = 1  ← ответ",
          "style": {
            "stroke": "#27ae60",
            "stroke_width": 2.5
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}